            <head>"THE BLACK FINGER"</head>
            
            <lg>
               <l>I have just seen a most beautiful thing</l>
               <l>Slim and still,</l>
               <l rend="i3">Against a gold, gold sky,</l>
               <l rend="i2">A straight black cypress,</l>
               <l rend="i2">Sensitive,</l>
               <l rend="i3">Exquisite,</l>
               <l rend="i3">A black finger</l>
               <l>Pointing upwards.</l>
               <l>Why, beautiful still finger, are you black?</l>
               <l>And why are you pointing upwards?</l>
            </lg>

            <byline>-Angelina Grimke</byline>
         </div>
